Package me.philcali.device.pool.reservation

Interface ReservationService

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DeviceLabProvisionService, Ec2ReservationService, LocalProvisionService
    public interface ReservationService
extends AutoCloseable
    The injection point for describing data path details for a provision request. The provisioning workflow will initialize reservation details for the intent of establishing data paths. The ReservationService exchanges initialized Reservation details for complete data paths. The data path is materialized in the form of a Host to facilitate reachability in various data plane components, namely the Connection and ContentTransferAgent.
